🔴 [P1 CRITICAL] Reconciliation avg is above 30 seconds

avg duration: {{value}}s
The ArgoCD controller is taking too long to reconcile applications.
This may indicate cluster API slowness, too many resources, or controller resource starvation.

Actions:
1. Check controller CPU/memory on the Host Cluster dashboard
2. Check work queue depth: should not be growing
3. Review controller logs for timeout errors
4. Check if specific apps are causing slow reconciliation
